 we want machines to understand.","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2117","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/padrino/padrino-framework","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2117/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2117/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2117/events","html_url":"https://github.com/padrino/padrino-framework/issues/2117","id":201735767,"number":2117,"title":"WARNING! In Padrino >= 0.14.0 cli command `padrino rake` will NOT add './lib' folder to $LOAD_PATH. Please alter your `require` calls accordingly","user":{"login":"bigtunacan","id":1995168,"avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/1995168?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan","html_url":"https://github.com/bigtunacan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bigtunacan/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2017-01-19T00:55:33Z","updated_at":"2017-07-13T21:07:26Z","closed_at":"2017-01-19T06:01:27Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"In the latest version of Padrino I am receiving this WARNING\r\n\r\n`WARNING! In Padrino >= 0.14.0 cli command `padri